            "stars": 5,
            "stars_color": "#018e1c",
            "title": "Amazing customer service",
            "body": "<p>Aside from their product being great (been helping me get better more consistent nights of sleep) -- their customer service is Excellent. Throughout any of my ordering questions or needs -- they are quick to respond. Definitely have that family owned -- \"We Care About You\" Customer Service attitude. Highly recommend them!</p>",
            "author_name": "Michael P.",
            "badge_type": "unprompted"
          }
        },
